{"tid":1076663,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果地鐵撞車 係撞個下跳起係咪就會無事？","createTime":"2019-03-25T04:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T05:19:27.000Z","uid":203714,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f09a4a15b953b67f489c8de3c4c361b1d19abd94","tid":1076663,"uid":203714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b119f2c385f1543d9cb90cba4c49e4b57a38bb0f","tid":1076663,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"撞得仲甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5faea24b721688e1c06bfcf54c40c8a9eccb358","tid":1076663,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"你個人會飛前，撞向前面既野，就好似你企係行緊高速公路既巴士車頂，撞落天橋咁甘"},{"pid":"47c0b89dc703a385240eca6bc0adb06aedb05fd8","tid":1076663,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"墜機先係<br />\n地鐵撞車要向後跳"},{"pid":"e934b478926e8658b9ea02ff95a555b2f12ada83","tid":1076663,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大前提係你要知架車幾時對撞，分秒不差"},{"pid":"24daaaba1586109a2dd18a1a9399ad9783ab5c49","tid":1076663,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"要即刻向後跑，之後撞嗰一刻就跳起，假如你速度夠快就冇事"},{"pid":"ae8630b673618bed5676ed88bc4f01718c7ee458","tid":1076663,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"你會比架車既速度影響左咖<br />\n等於架地鐵將你向前拋 再接返你<br />\n而唔係你可以直上直落<br />\n<br />\n當你平時搭地鐵有ABC三個位<br />\n你係B位跳 都唔會去到C位"},{"pid":"96120249b5e95b750c163050d5e7af7c86a74101","tid":1076663,"uid":101128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"中學讀好d physics唔該 會救你一命"}]}